yea well i went up north last thurday and was up there for the forth...it was really fun! they weather was nice the first 4 days and then it got really cold and rainy but we still had lots of fun! yea and then on one of the cold but nicer day me and my cousin erica decide to go riding on the four wheeler and let me remind u we have no licences on them and yea so where going and we decide to go to my grandmas cottage which is outta the woods and about a mile away so where going and we get there and then come back so where going up this hill on the "highway" (only like 5 cars go on it a day) and im leading and i look and i see this truck so i yell to erica to move over so we did and i was like dude is this guy gonna pass...so i look behind us and the bastard turns his god damn lights on...so yea were busted its a fucking undercover cop....WTF he asked us to get off the bikes and asked us all this shit... man we was about to run but i would have went in a ditch if i had ran ! so he ended followin us back to our cabin and thats when hell broke lose...haha not my uncle talked to him and was like give em a break and flashed his fireman badge...haha yea so me and erica r now nicknamed nicole and paris...lmao wtf 
but it was crazy i had so much fun!! but yea now im home and it sux  ...

PEace
